<span class="headers">Learn Fletching</span>
<p>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="3">
<tr>
<td><a href="http://www.gucomics.com/archives/view.php?cdate=20000716"><img src="http://www.eqtraders.com/images/articles/gu_20000716.jpg" width="200" height="300" border="0" align="left" /></a></td>

<td>
<p class="mainbody">Using the fletching skill, a player may make bows and arrows of better quality, range and damage than what can be purchased from a merchant. </p>

<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g26&menustr=040050000000">Fletching</a> - by Quon</li>
