<li><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Fletching&menustr=110060000000">EQTC listing of fletching supply merchants by zone</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=39&rsa=Fletching&sb=item&sub=&menustr=080060000000">EQTC fletching recipes</a></li>
<li><a href="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/aoenla/fletchguide/" target="_new">Aeonla's Fletching Guide</a> is no longer updated, but it's still one of the most comprehensive fletching sites out there.</li>
</ul>

</td>
